{"parentUuid": null, "isSidechain": false, "promptId": "prompt-7207b1f8", "type": "user", "message": {"role": "user", "content": "I'm getting `Property 'session' does not exist on type 'NextRequest'` in middleware. Where do I extend the type?"}, "uuid": "7207b1f8-2d45-4981-bc95-1b690e6e81dc", "timestamp": "2026-05-04T10:00:30.000Z", "isMeta": false, "userType": "external", "entrypoint": "cli", "cwd": "/Users/alex/code/nextjs-app", "sessionId": "4cc786ab-af25-4e06-86b0-b7b6bce22306", "version": "2.0.0", "gitBranch": "main"}
{"parentUuid": "7207b1f8-2d45-4981-bc95-1b690e6e81dc", "isSidechain": false, "message": {"model": "claude-sonnet-4-6", "id": "msg_39eb81cd-3eb", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "You augment the module declaration. Create `types/next.d.ts`:\n\n```ts\nimport 'next/server';\n\ndeclare module 'next/server' {\n  interface NextRequest {\n    session?: { userId: string; expiresAt: Date };\n  }\n}\n```\n\nThen make sure `tsconfig.json` has `\"include\": [\"types/**/*.d.ts\", ...]`. Restart the TS server in your editor \u2014 it caches declarations aggressively."}], "stop_reason": "end_turn", "usage": {"input_tokens": 320, "output_tokens": 227, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 0}}, "requestId": "req_0163c2e7-e07", "type": "assistant", "uuid": "20790637-fd38-4ad0-9788-aa07eebf394e", "timestamp": "2026-05-04T10:00:36.000Z", "userType": "external", "entrypoint": "cli", "cwd": "/Users/alex/code/nextjs-app", "sessionId": "4cc786ab-af25-4e06-86b0-b7b6bce22306", "version": "2.0.0", "gitBranch": "main"}
